{"tid":2410223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"漁護署情人節巡查郊野公園發現違例露營 向違反限聚令人士發出定額罰款通知書","createTime":"2021-02-16T12:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T13:13:28.000Z","uid":19287,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fee36725efd0d5dc27b41935a31fe2b95782473","tid":2410223,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"政府部門因應疫情而暫時關閉郊野公園燒烤及露營地點，不過仍有不少市民在假期會選擇遠離市區到郊區露營。漁農自然護理署轄下FB專頁「郊野公園教育活動計劃」日前就撰文提醒市民不要在郊野公園露營，透露情人節當日巡查郊野公園期間向24名違例露營人士採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n郊野公園教育活動計劃」在2月14日情人節當晚出POST，提醒市民目前郊野公園燒烤及露營地點繼續暫停開放。漁護署工作人員在情人節當日巡查郊野公園，向24名違例露營人士採取執法行動，包括向當中13名違反限聚令人士發出定額罰款通知書。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVo6CSA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVo6CSA.jpg&h=830a69b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFP2bcB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFP2bcB.jpg&h=fb9ba3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJdeMLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJdeMLZ.jpg&h=3ba079ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c1720a9e9bf07913d14311cbf8acc510690b15f","tid":2410223,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"咁L 陰濕"},{"pid":"ba6f26a7c925d08a3fdefc230102b9d89f528613","tid":2410223,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:16:47.000Z","msg":"應該夜晚做至好，順便照田雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436faed2f70bb942986959cb5823dcf99fb65bbf","tid":2410223,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"又搶錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53b96d2f557bde50ca83a3e51939b15bcf7c75b","tid":2410223,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><